description:
DESNZ is seeking supplier(s) to deliver research on opportunities for effective and responsible research and/or deployment of non-CCS reliant GGRs, including biochar, enhanced weathering (EW) and marine carbon dioxide removal (mCDR), over timescales relevant to meeting our carbon budgets and net zero targets.  
The programme will provide targeted evidence for near-term policy milestones, examining: 
the real-world performance of these GGRs;  
approaches to monitoring, reporting and verification;
